OL,3,CCalls for Ballycastle hotel to be
OL,4,Cpreserved for 'historic restoration'
OL,6,FThe Antrim Arms hotel has stood in
OL,7,FBallycastle's Diamond for generations.
OL,8,FBut it's been left to crack and
OL,9,Fcrumble over the last 10 years.
OL,11,FThe building is owned by Maplemanor
OL,12,FProperties, which is controlled by
OL,13,FAntrim-based businessman Declan Joseph
OL,14,FWright.
