OL,3,CCalls for Ballycastle hotel to be
OL,4,Cpreserved for 'historic restoration'
OL,6,FThey recently made an application to
OL,7,FCauseway Coast and Glens Borough
OL,8,FCouncil to demolish the building,
OL,9,Fwhich the council says it is currently
OL,10,Fstudying. Stating that any attempt to
OL,11,Fpartially demolish and restore it
OL,12,Fwould cost in excess of #1m. Something
OL,13,Fthe developer says it cannot afford.
OL,15,FFull demolition it says would cost a
OL,16,Ffraction of the price and minimise
OL,17,Fdisruption to the town.
