OL,3,CCalls for Ballycastle hotel to be
OL,4,Cpreserved for 'historic restoration'
OL,6,FAlliance North Antrim MLA Sian
OL,7,FMulholland lives in Ballycastle and is
OL,8,Ffirmly against any demolition: " I'd
OL,9,Flove to see it restored to its full
OL,10,Fglory. "I've seen the pictures when
OL,11,Fthe Antrim Arms was at its best and I
OL,12,Fwould absolutely love to see a
OL,13,Fsympathetic historical restoration."
OL,15,FMrs Mulholland adds: "You can look
OL,16,Faround you. You can see what
OL,17,FBallycastle was, generations have come
OL,18,Fthrough this town and it is really
OL,19,Fimportant, particularly for those
OL,20,Frural towns and villages to keep that
OL,21,Fheart, to keep that heritage.
